des: Say wake me up, wake up,or wake somebody up to use the first option. say wake me up again, wake up again, wake somebody up again for the second option. say please wake me up, please wake up, please wake somebody up for option three. Say play song 1 for option , play song 2 for option 2, and play song 3 for option 3. These are for just listening to the music. Sorry for how fast Alexa sings the songs, Alexa is very specific about the format which mess up the song. Hope you enjoy the Wake up bot.
